videos.headline: UCF's Griffin recovers fumble
videos.description: Darrell Henderson throws an off target pitch which hits the ground and is recovered by UCF's Shaquem Griffin.

videos.headline: UCF's Milton tosses 25-yard TD to Snelson
videos.description: McKenzie Milton hits Dredrick Snelson for the first touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Taylor puts Memphis on the board
videos.description: Patrick Taylor Jr. punches in a 3-yard touchdown for the first Memphis score of the game.

videos.headline: UCF's Milton hits Akins for 48-yard TD
videos.description: McKenzie Milton finds a wide open Jordan Akins, who takes it 48 yards to the house.

videos.headline: Pollard grabs TD for Memphis
videos.description: Riley Ferguson throws a 13-yard touchdown pass to Tony Pollard.

videos.headline: Smith brings in 50-yard UCF TD
videos.description: McKenzie Milton throws to Tre'Quan Smith in stride who takes it 50 yards for another UCF touchdown.

videos.headline: Memphis recovers Snelson's fumble
videos.description: Dredrick Snelson makes the catch, but fumbles on the run for UCF's first turnover of the game.

videos.headline: Henderson breaks off 30-yard TD
videos.description: Darrell Henderson takes the hand off 30 yards for a Memphis touchdown.

videos.headline: Miller goes up the sideline for 68-yard TD
videos.description: Anthony Miller takes the Riley Ferguson pass 68 yards up the sideline for a Memphis touchdown.

videos.headline: Memphis' Carter intercepts Milton in the end zone
videos.description: McKenzie Milton throws a red zone inteception to Terrell Carter.

videos.headline: Frost: Turnovers have to stop
videos.description: UCF head coach Scott Frost says his team has to stop turning the ball over in the second half in order to beat Memphis.

videos.headline: Milton keeps it for 16-yard TD
videos.description: McKenzie Milton runs it up the middle for a 16-yard UCF touchdown.

videos.headline: UCF's Milton airs it out for 34-yard TD
videos.description: Tre'Quan Smith leaps to grab McKenzie Milton's fourth touchdown pass of the game.

videos.headline: Milton makes 28-yard TD throw on the run
videos.description: McKenzie Milton rolls out and delivers a touchdown pass to a diving Dredrick Snelson to extend the UCF lead.

videos.headline: Pollard goes off for 66-yard TD
videos.description: Tony Pollard brings Memphis within seven with a 66-yard fourth quarter touchdown.

videos.headline: Ferguson's TD evens the score
videos.description: Riley Ferguson tosses a 10-yard touchdown pass to Anthony Miller for Memphis to tie the game at 48-48.

videos.headline: Henderson picks up 36 yards on 3rd-and-long
videos.description: Darrell Henderson comes up with a huge run for a Memphis first down.

videos.headline: Cook's INT sends game to OT
videos.description: McKenzie Milton throws his third interception of the game to Memphis' Jonathan Cook with 14 seconds left.

videos.headline: Ferguson throws first TD in OT
videos.description: Riley Ferguson throws a 15-yard touchdown to Anthony Miller for Memphis.

videos.headline: Killins dives for TD in OT
videos.description: Adrian Killins Jr. dives toward the pylon to send the game to a second overtime.

videos.headline: Anderson forces in TD
videos.description: Otis Anderson gets in the end zone on a second effort to give UCF the overtime lead.

videos.headline: Frost: I'm going to celebrate with my team
videos.description: Scott Frost talks to Todd McShay after his UCF team completes an undefeated regular season.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Frost: I'm going to celebrate with my team) 2017/12/2

videos.headline: Neal's INT seals a UCF win
videos.description: Tre Neal intercepts Riley Ferguson in the second overtime to clinch the American Athletic Conference championship for UCF.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Neal's INT seals a UCF win) 2017/12/2

videos.headline: UCF wins AAC title
videos.description: Steve Levy and Brian Griese break down UCF's double overtime win in the American Athletic Conference championship game and what bowl game the Knights could be headed to.

videos.headline: Who had the better interception?
videos.description: Who had the better interception on Saturday, Clemson's Kendall Joseph or UCF's Tre Neal?

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Who had the better interception?) 2017/12/2 ESHEET ENHL
